The paper deals with a subspace embedding technique and its application to linear regression with Orlicz norm. This involves concepts from information theory (cs.IT), machine learning (cs.LG), numerical analysis (cs.NA), data structures (cs.DS), and signal processing (cs.SI). Therefore, these are the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper.
